rl":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemebadgecomponenttokensprovider\/sizesmall","kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeBadgeComponentTokensProvider\/sizeSmall","title":"sizeSmall","type":"topic","abstract":[{"text":"Has for value token dimensions._6xsmall","type":"text"}],"fragments":[{"text":"var","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"sizeSmall","kind":"identifier"},{"text":": ","kind":"text"},{"text":"SizeSemanticToken","preciseIdentifier":"s:18OUDSTokensSemantic04SizeB5Tokena","kind":"typeIdentifier"}],"role":"symbol"},"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange/OrangeThemeBadgeComponentTokensProvider":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeBadgeComponentTokensProvider","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"OrangeThemeBadgeComponentTokensProvider","kind":"identifier"}],"kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemebadgecomponenttokensprovider","title":"OrangeThemeBadgeComponentTokensProvider","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OrangeThemeBadgeComponentTokensProvider","kind":"identifier"}],"type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A class which wraps all "},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"component  tokens of badge"}]},{"type":"text","text":" for "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"badge","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" objects like "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSBadge"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Contains also references to semantic tokens providers so as to be able to use them to define the component tokens."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"This provider should be integrated as a "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllBadgeComponentTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation inside "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to provide"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"all tokens to the users. It helps users to override some of the tokens and assign them to an "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":" implementation to use."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Custom themes can use subclass of "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeBadgeComponentTokensProvider","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" and apply the provider they need."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"It implements also the protocol "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"BadgeComponentTokens"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to expose the component tokens for "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"badge","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" through any "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"Badge","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" components tokens are defined with semantic tokens of dimensions ("},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllDimensionSemanticTokensProviders"},{"type":"text","text":"),"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"and spaces (from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllSpaceSemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":")."}]},"doc://OUDSThemesOrange/documentation/OUDSThemesOrange":{"title":"Theme Orange","images":[{"identifier":"ic_theme_orange.png","type":"icon"}],"abstract":[{"text":"The Orange theme overrides some tokens from the basic ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"text":" and should be seen as the default theme for the OUDS library with the Orange brand colors for example.","type":"text"}],"kind":"symbol","role":"collection","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange","url":"\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange","type":"topic"}}}